# EmailJS Credentials Template
# 1. Create a file named ".env" in this root folder.
# 2. Sign up on https://www.emailjs.com/ (free tier provides 200 emails/month).
# 3. Add an Email Service linked to your personal email, and create an Email Template.
# 4. Copy your credentials into the ".env" file as shown below:

VITE_EMAILJS_SERVICE_ID=your_service_id_here
VITE_EMAILJS_TEMPLATE_ID=your_template_id_here
VITE_EMAILJS_PUBLIC_KEY=your_public_key_here
